Michael Nader https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Nader 0 Michael Nader (born February 19, 1945) is an American actor, known for his roles as Dex Dexter on the ABC primetime soap opera Dynasty from 1983 to 1989, and Dimitri Marick on the ABC daytime soap opera All My Children from 1991 to 2001, and in 2013.
